c4a977689d888a3","tid":677814,"uid":79563,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拆局：美朝峰會告吹 分析指中國或成大贏家<br />\n　2018-05-25 20:39<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png&h=2d0825c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美朝峰會未能實現，有美國傳媒分析認為，北韓在事件中「計錯數」，多番言論過火累事。反為中國則可能成為大贏家，因為中方一直不願意美朝走得太近，以免失去對北韓的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n正當全球期待美國總統特朗普與北韓領袖金正恩，下月十二日在新加坡舉行峰會之際，特朗普突然宣布取消會面。<br />\n<br />\n美國媒體認為，北韓副外長崔善姬批評美國副總統彭斯將北韓與利比亞相提並論，是愚昧無知的言論，成為美朝峰會觸礁的「最後一根稻草」。<br />\n<br />\n但特朗普近日的言論亦暗示，峰會能否實現的癥結，是金正恩近期兩度訪華，與國家主席習近平會面。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示：「北韓在這次會議(大連會面)後，態度有變，事態亦有變，所以我不能說我對此感到高興。」<br />\n<br />\n西方分析員認為，中朝是共產主義道路上的傳統盟友，北韓單獨與美國修好，對中國有一定影響。<br />\n<br />\n外交分析員斯塔夫里迪斯稱：「中國會覺得與北韓之間關係中斷，如果峰會缺乏了中國參與。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/story/5abb563ae603835a5287773c/5b080404e60383c437935edb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fstory%2F5abb563ae603835a5287773c%2F5b080404e60383c437935edb%2F&d=cbF0bS4pKh3BDNQfrBLWC%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=96767a3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/story/5abb563ae603835a5287773c/5b080404e60383c437935edb/</a><br />\n<br />\n有內地專家則另有看法，指中國樂見各方簽訂朝鮮半島和平協議，以免美朝一旦發生軍事衝突，會波及中國，而更重要的是，在「太平盛世」下，美國再無藉口在南韓駐軍，美軍一旦撤走，勢必大大削減美國在亞洲區內的影響力，對中國來說更為有利。<br />\n下一則：美國單方面取消與北韓峰會 中方籲美朝保持耐心"},{"pid":"18e515cfb0ff700ae609fe2aebfead716a2c1929","tid":677814,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oriNMh2ZOk9m6EOQ0/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oriNMh2ZOk9m6EOQ0%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e77dd86f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4b25469ff661793fc6c29943aef80eba0ad3253","tid":677814,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3ae900a5a51a9c561d683f7e89faea6fc1d25aee","tid":677814,"uid":27146,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家，呢點點都唔會炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"[CCTVB]<br />\n<br />\n美朝峰會如期舉行   中國或成最大贏家<br />\n<br />\n[/CCTVB]"},{"pid":"bb0407fe4d45724f2cf800dc46a06d561c0280e3","tid":677814,"uid":48,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:16:10.000Z","msg":"點捉到TRUMP咩玩法<br />\n<br />\n一時一樣"},{"pid":"4dfc58a67dc8b8b07d053950a2e03508ffcccb32","tid":677814,"uid":182475,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:16:27.000Z","msg":"記得開埋霧燈"},{"pid":"0186e8b8ba9d5e7cd95092d73d1b00fde326c420","tid":677814,"uid":7245,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"CLS 玩撚夠未呀 成個世界俾你搞灣哂啦"},{"pid":"9f552585c25759acb9b5568be486e1be231a6115","tid":677814,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"頭搖又尾擺"},{"pid":"b67bdcebafc468fd122959fd3d90dfdcbf5b6756","tid":677814,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"習帝唔想美朝順利開WOR  一"},{"pid":"92879d681affd7b605153ffc4609a0887238779c","tid":677814,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1907f54e049c9b7271f4ac7aa55391a7139bd2e","tid":677814,"uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20