7689d888a3","tid":677814,"uid":79563,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拆局：美朝峰會告吹 分析指中國或成大贏家<br />\n　2018-05-25 20:39<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F205748_78868c8648febd268e89e0dc8c908a53.png&h=2d0825c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美朝峰會未能實現，有美國傳媒分析認為，北韓在事件中「計錯數」，多番言論過火累事。反為中國則可能成為大贏家，因為中方一直不願意美朝走得太近，以免失去對北韓的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n正當全球期待美國總統特朗普與北韓領袖金正恩，下月十二日在新加坡舉行峰會之際，特朗普突然宣布取消會面。<br />\n<br />\n美國媒體認為，北韓副外長崔善姬批評美國副總統彭斯將北韓與利比亞相提並論，是愚昧無知的言論，成為美朝峰會觸礁的「最後一根稻草」。<br />\n<br />\n但特朗普近日的言論亦暗示，峰會能否實現的癥結，是金正恩近期兩度訪華，與國家主席習近平會面。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示：「北韓在這次會議(大連會面)後，態度有變，事態亦有變，所以我不能說我對此感到高興。」<br />\n<br />\n西方分析員認為，中朝是共產主義道路上的傳統盟友，北韓單獨與美國修好，對中國有一定影響。<br />\n<br />\n外交分析員斯塔夫里迪斯稱：「中國會覺得與北韓之間關係中斷，如果峰會缺乏了中國參與。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/story/5abb563ae603835a5287773c/5b080404e60383c437935edb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fstory%2F5abb563ae603835a5287773c%2F5b080404e60383c437935edb%2F&d=cbF0bS4pKh3BDNQfrBLWC%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=96767a3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/story/5abb563ae603835a5287773c/5b080404e60383c437935edb/</a><br />\n<br />\n有內地專家則另有看法，指中國樂見各方簽訂朝鮮半島和平協議，以免美朝一旦發生軍事衝突，會波及中國，而更重要的是，在「太平盛世」下，美國再無藉口在南韓駐軍，美軍一旦撤走，勢必大大削減美國在亞洲區內的影響力，對中國來說更為有利。<br />\n下一則：美國單方面取消與北韓峰會 中方籲美朝保持耐心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"支那乜都贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375c6a3b51a5159fea098aeabf9fe70f230ea7dd","tid":677814,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劇情反轉再反轉"},{"pid":"9178bdfe9e2e537ca23b85a30b95b910656f2def","tid":677814,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1907f54e049c9b7271f4ac7aa55391a7139bd2e","tid":677814,"uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"Very good news to receive the warm and productive statement from North Korea. We will soon see where it will lead, hopefully to long and enduring prosperity and peace. Only time (and talent) will tell!<br />\n<br />\n話係金仔主動揾佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"其實兩條友係咪諗方法踢鳩開支那，但又要做得好好睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾籍口金仔飛佢<br />\n侵侵又扮晒有大佬風範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabb6d8399b2a283b30004705a03edcc08798d74","tid":677814,"uid":39221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"啱啱又有風放出黎話金仔又去見維尼喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1d2795a14d11fa6ed799f49919330da6e490e2","tid":677814,"uid":46014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"侵仔教緊大家溝女<br />\n欲擒故縱<br />\n一啖砂糖一啖屎"},{"pid":"3d07479d2b5441736a78eea05a843163ecce1096","tid":677814,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64bc48596641404e1719e8862797bcc4480d304e","tid":677814,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eabb6d8399b2a283b30004705a03edcc08798d74","tid":677814,"uid":39221,"like":1,"dislike